0w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2023_noelgallagher_-mattcrockett_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2023_noelgallagher_-mattcrockett_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2023_noelgallagher_-mattcrockett_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2023_noelgallagher_-mattcrockett_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/NOEL-GALLAGHER">诺尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher)</a>分享了他的新单曲“We&#39;re Gonna Get There In The End”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/noel-gallagher-interview-oasis-council-skies-3451058">诺埃尔·加拉格尔（Noel Gallagher）：“世界是一个美丽的地方——只是居住着混蛋”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌曲取自他最近的专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds-council-skies-review-3450645">《Council Skies》</a> ，是继他之前的单曲《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds">High Flying Birds</a> 》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds-open-the-door-see-what-you-find-with-johnny-marr-3449952#:~:text=Discussing%20the%20meaning%20behind%20the,will%20pave%20out%20for%20them.">《Open The Door, See What You Find》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-noel-gallaghers-rousing-new-single-council-skies-3433136">主打歌</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-noel-gallaghers-melancholic-new-single-dead-to-the-world-3419571">《Dead To The World》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-announces-new-album-council-skies-releases-single-easy-now-listen-preorder-3381946">《Easy Now</a> 》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-noel-gallaghers-new-song-pretty-boy-featuring-johnny-marr-3339249">《Pretty》</a>之后的歌曲。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-noel-gallaghers-new-song-pretty-boy-featuring-johnny-marr-3339249">男孩</a>。</p><p>谈到这首歌，加拉格尔说：“我在大流行期间的一个晚上写了这首歌。我写了它并发布了演示。我想要一些积极向上的东西——只是一首真实的、令人振奋的曲调。作为一名艺术家，封锁期间的时间让你可以专注于一些事情。但这并没有让那段时间变得更容易。”</p><p> 《We&#39;re Gonna Get There In The End》最初于 2020 年除夕夜作为演示曲发布，后来成为他 2023 年专辑的最后一首曲目。您可以收听和观看该视频，其中包含他今年夏天在曼彻斯特威森肖公园演出的片段，如下所示。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify Embed：我们最终会实现这一目标" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="152" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/2gsIQEPa5Bvbqtx54isJC9?go=1&#038;nd=1&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 的 High Flying Birds - 我们最终会到达那里（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0-lZVmy4Gy4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">绿洲</a>人和他的高飞鸟队将于下个月上路进行竞技场巡演。任何剩余的巡演门票（包括伦敦温布利 OVO 竞技场的日期）都可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fnoel-gallagher-s-high-flying-birds-tickets%2Fartist%2F1637030" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买。</p><p>与此同时，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格尔</a>最近声称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-says-noel-gallagher-turned-down-definitely-maybe-tour-3516455">诺埃尔拒绝了参加即将举行的“Definitely Maybe”巡演的机会</a>。</p><p> “有人邀请他，但他拒绝了，”他在回答一位粉丝询问他何时宣布诺埃尔参与巡演时写道。</p><p>利亚姆还分享了他对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-gives-his-verdict-on-the-beatles-final-song-now-and-then-3528896">期待已久的“最后一首歌”的评价</a>——透露他发现这首歌“温暖人心”。</p><p> “现在和那时绝对是令人难以置信的圣经天国令人心碎和温暖的同时，”他在今天早上的第一篇文章中写道。 “披头士乐队万岁。”</p><p>这首歌<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-beatles-final-song-now-and-then-3529039">随后于格林尼治标准时间下午 2 点首演</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liverpools-jacaranda-club-hosts-emotional-beatles-listening-party-for-now-and-then-3529240">在利物浦的蓝花楹俱乐部举办了一场聆听派对</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-shares-new-single-were-gonna-get-there-in-the-end-3529328">Noel Gallagher 分享新单曲《We&#39;re Gonna Get There In The End》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
